                    "message": {
                        "text": "Reentrancy in FinancialPoolManager._selectWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#213-270):\n\tExternal calls:\n\t- (success,None) = winner.call{value: p.goodValue}() (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#264)\n\tState variables written after the call(s):\n\t- p.status = finished (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#268)\n\tFinancialPoolManager.pools (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#46) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- FinancialPoolManager._selectWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#213-270)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.activatePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#93-111)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.createPool(string,uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#68-90)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.deletePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#114-127)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#277-307)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.leavePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#149-169)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.onlyOwner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#58-61)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.participateInPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#134-146)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#176-207)\n"
